sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User
  participant API as FastAPI (/answer)
  participant RET as Hybrid Retrieve
  participant BM as BM25
  participant DEN as Dense (Chroma)
  participant RER as Reranker (opt)
  participant LLM as Generator (opt)

  U->>API: POST /answer {q,k,use_reranker,use_bm25}
  API->>RET: retrieve_with_timings(q)
  par Parallel
    RET->>BM: topK ids
    RET->>DEN: dense similarity
  end
  RET->>RET: MMR (diversify to k)
  RET-->>API: candidates + timings

  alt use_reranker == true
    API->>RER: rerank(q, candidates)
    RER-->>API: top 8
  else
    API-->>API: skip reranker
  end

  alt generator configured
    API->>LLM: prompt with citations
    LLM-->>API: answer text
  else
    API-->>API: degraded message (citations only)
  end

  API-->>U: {text, citations, timings, retrieve_breakdown}
